# Kilo
.kilo/plans/*upstream-merge-report-*.md
.kilo/*.log
# NOTE: .kilo/governance.json is intentionally TRACKED — it is the canonical
# state file loaded by GovernanceService at startup. It is also written-to at
# runtime by the running Hub server, so expect drift in `git status` while the
# Hub is running. Do not `git rm --cached` it: fresh clones rely on the
# committed defaults (the loader does fall back to DEFAULT_STATE, but the
# tracked file is the canonical source). To suppress drift locally during a
# session, stash or restore: `git restore .kilo/governance.json`.

# Runtime artifacts written by services/Hub (logs, status caches, state files)
backend/artifacts/services/*.log
backend/artifacts/services/*-cache.json
backend/artifacts/services/_*_cache.json
backend/artifacts/services/*-status.json
backend/artifacts/services/*-state.json
